  "instructions": [
    "Combine dijon mustard and apple cider vinegar in a small bowl. Mix in maple syrup until smooth.",
    "Add all-purpose flour to the mustard mixture while stirring continuously until thickened and smooth.",
    "Season with celery salt, kosher salt, white pepper, and mixed herbs.",
    "Place flaked salmon on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper. Spoon the sauce over each piece of salmon evenly.",
    "Bake in a preheated oven at 350°F (175°C) for about 15 minutes or until cooked through."
